Title: Le Socrate
Writer: Colette Audry (dialogue), Robert Lapoujade, Jean-Patrick Manchette (dialogue)
Actors: Pierre Luzan, René-Jean Chauffard, Martine Brochard, Stéphane Fay
Plot: Shows the eccentricties of Le Socrate, a philosopher who has divorced himself from materialistic society and a local policeman assigned to watch him.
